{"type": "article", "id": 22980, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-02-29T07:03:08Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 24107, "name": "甜品包装"}, {"id": 2976, "name": "灯饰"}, {"id": 24108, "name": "Folkform"}, {"id": 24109, "name": "Paul Matter"}, {"id": 24110, "name": "Design Womb"}, {"id": 24111, "name": "ODDO Studio"}, {"id": 24112, "name": "Diiis"}, {"id": 24113, "name": "Ragnheiður Ösp Sigurðardóttir"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 34, "image": "img/article/article_show/2016060717430928ZpIfeNPrbQckXB.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p>\n<h2>Revolving Bookcases  by Folkform </h2>\n<p>这是由瑞典设家居品牌 Folkform 推出的一组可旋转的书架，像一个小的茶几或床头柜。他们使用了一种烧焦的木头，在可旋转的中轴上安装了一个立方体空间，像一个个小的窗口，每一面都不一样。 Folkform 的设计师认为人们会越来越需要实体书，相比于将书陈列在大的书架里，会更倾向挑选少量自己喜欢的书放在小的书架中。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153525ntl68ywPDq3JK2Bx.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153525abeU784RjEYoyN0Z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.09615385\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153526i3ahLkm6nQSYesbT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071535267hmb9WENM15iDqtA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Seed by Diiis</h2>\n<p>这是一个木质首饰盒，来自瑞典设计师  Diiis 。小山一样的盖子也有展示戒指和项链的功能，揭开后有一面圆镜和圆形的小碟一样的储存空间。浅色的木材表面还有细小的纹路，让这个首饰盒格外温润，可以放在门厅、卧室等多个空间中。<a href=\"http://www.diiis.ch/products/sedo\">这里是工作室主页，</a>他们有另一款与此类似的首饰盒设计。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153526sGKZmt0YbukypzWj.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153527EaHqAgvrLRVnfpNz.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153527vW92EQY5brhV4N8B.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153528rjiyO0NHJZ7lb1Y3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153528UlxYRJtksVKvIg73.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66574074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2> TANGO by Paul Matter</h2>\n<p>这是印度新德里一家新成立的灯具品牌 Paul Matter 在推出的一组产品，包括两个灯具和一个蜡烛台。产品都使用了黄铜材料体现出传统和复古的色彩，特征在于灯具的悬挂杆的下面是可调整的，使灯具的朝向有了倾斜的角度，搭配相互交错的挂杆，立刻让这组灯有了艺术气息，也能表达出使用者的个性。<a href=\"http://www.paulmatter.com\">这里是该品牌的主页。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153528X6VQOPSvZnBawi0c.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153529FC4U30PiuhGJl6cS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153529NJ6cy0X8GgW1hOLu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153530V32fgtirdeA1jkov.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70740741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153530I4QqpHBMGWTVaRmg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<h2>Umemi's Sold Items by Ragnheiður Ösp Sigurðardóttir</h2>\n<p>这是冰岛设计师  Ragnheiður Ösp Sigurðardóttir 带来的抱枕，它的灵感源于中国结。根据不同的打结方式，它也有丰富的形状，使用者甚至可以自行拆掉还原成一条粗线，然后重新打结，手工感十足。这些抱枕的表面都是由不同颜色的毛线织成，中间塞入填充，非常温暖居家。目前在 easy 上出售，<a href=\"https://www.etsy.com/shop/Umemi/sold?ref=shopinfo_sales_leftnav\">这里是购买链接</a>。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153531EmZodOaSDszA83ly.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74769231\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153531n3FsxDRK15dUWc78.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153531v2tMcmr9G1WPxlAZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74307692\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153532fRojZgBKXEYpOH9L.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.00153846\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153532fT5o8Wc9izbVFNtp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56153846\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<h2>SALAD MAKING by ODDO Studio</h2>\n<p>这两片像叶子一样的工具集中了切割和搅拌沙拉等多个功能。其中一片下面的轮廓带有齿轮，两只手各拿一片时，以另一片的中间为板，可以实现简单的快速切割。切割好的蔬果放在碗中，这两个工具正好像大勺一样搅拌沙拉。产品目前还是一个概念。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153533lrJT3jUKfFRPWoeN.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71714286\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071535335esNVg6P03jCS98O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75047619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153534gqZYDrTFXcSuNlvi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153534jvqDwIWEpokJgTdK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71809524\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153535iFPT2qvOcgHV0tNJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75047619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016060715353504J9IKemlgZa3COL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.1952381\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<h2>Green Girl Bakeshop by Design Womb</h2>\n<p>这是一组“冰淇淋三明治”（ice cream sandwiches）的甜品包装设计，选用了清新而略带复古的风格。立方体的盒子以黑白两色为主，间隔有彩色的点缀来表现不同的口味。纸质的包装使用了黑白网格，就像野餐时需要打开的布，上面贴有荷叶边的标签让这它多了一份童真和可爱。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153536CuAOMTnqpmY2varK.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153536wdF4L6DYyMJAGO3H.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153537MI21L5SZWcD0Nap7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153537p9CgebxUWZ2TqnEt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153538IA8lw93kcbaieSzr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.61481481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n"}